---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import VisitorCounter from '../components/VisitorCounter.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Gil Gatson - Entrepreneur, Business Strategist, and Author"
  description="Entrepreneur obsessed with tech, geopolitics & winning the industrial future. Semicon wars. AI dominance. No time for cope."
>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Gil Gatson</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Entrepreneur obsessed with tech, geopolitics & winning the industrial future.<br>
        Semicon wars. AI dominance. No time for cope.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="featured-book">
      <h2>Latest Book</h2>
      <div class="book-card">
        <div class="book-cover">
          <img src="/covers/ai-delusion.jpg" alt="THE AI DELUSION book cover" width="300" height="450" />
        </div>
        <div class="book-info">
          <h3>THE AI DELUSION</h3>
          <p class="book-subtitle">The Brutal Truth About America's AI Future</p>
          <p class="book-description">
            Is America's AI leadership a dangerous illusion? While America celebrates its AI prowess, a dangerous delusion has taken hold. 
            The prevailing narrative of untouchable technological dominance is a mirage, masking a brutal truth about the real state of the global AI race.
          </p>
          <p class="book-description">
            In THE AI DELUSION, Gil Gatson pulls back the curtain on the critical vulnerabilities threatening America's future. 
            He exposes the five strategic bottlenecks Washington isn't talking about, the open-source trap that inadvertently aids our chief rival, 
            and how China is leveraging its manufacturing muscle and disciplined national strategy to gain a powerful asymmetric advantage.
          </p>
          <div class="book-links">
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GBVJX23D" class="btn">Kindle</a>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GBVJX23D" class="btn">Paperback</a>
            <a href="https://www.audible.com/pd/YOUR_AUDIOBOOK_ASIN" class="btn">Audiobook</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="books-preview">
      <h2>Side Hustle Launchpad Series</h2>
      <div class="books-grid">
        <div class="book-item">
          <h3>The TikTok Shop Launchpad</h3>
          <p>Launch your TikTok Shop business in 30 days with this step-by-step blueprint.</p>
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0G84HYJ1C">View on Amazon →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="book-item">
          <h3>Amazon KDP for Beginners</h3>
          <p>Publish your first book in a weekend with this practical guide to self-publishing.</p>
          <a href="/books#amazon-kdp">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="book-item">
          <h3>The Etsy Launchpad</h3>
          <p>Build a profitable Etsy business from scratch with proven strategies.</p>
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0G82BBYPL">View on Amazon →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="counter-wrapper">
      <VisitorCounter />
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem 5rem;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 0 -2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: 
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(41, 128, 185, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(142, 68, 173, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    
    .hero h1 {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 400;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    
    .bio {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    
    section {
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    
    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .featured-book {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 3rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    
    .book-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .book-cover img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 4px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .book-info h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .book-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: var(--color-gray);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .book-description {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .book-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: var(--color-accent);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background: #1d4ed8;
    }
    
    .books-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .book-item {
      padding: 2rem;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    
    .book-item h3 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .book-item a {
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .counter-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .book-card {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
      }
      
      .book-cover {
        max-width: 300px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      
      .featured-book {
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }
      
      .books-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
